{"tid":664954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飯鏟頭匿大廈信箱 警召蛇王生擒","createTime":"2018-05-14T13:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T13:49:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f0655142de3d7a68a6b9a8cce61bdb51d2197ee5","tid":664954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180514/20390638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390638&d=oSQATcPEiOS3RqyQsNV7tf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0c5458eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390638&h=4ea64ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180514/20390638</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月14日 <br />\n<br />\n飯鏟頭匿大廈信箱<br />\n警召蛇王生擒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】西環爹核士街38號先施西環大廈，昨日凌晨2時許，有住客返回大廈，發現大堂地下有一條蛇，立即通知看更報警。警員到場時，懷疑該蛇受驚，鑽入牆邊其中一格信箱內，捲縮起來。<br />\n<br />\n警員召蛇王到場，看更通知住戶用鎖匙開啓信箱，蛇王先用鈎試圖將蛇勾出來，但並不成功，其後拉著蛇尾，約5分鐘將其拉出及擒拿。據稱，該蛇兩呎長，是有毒的飯鏟頭，最後由蛇王撿走。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n昨晚六合彩開獎結果<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n退休第一個Sunday　李超人同陽光玩遊戲"}]}